data.description: Welcome to a charming 2-story farmhouse that combines rustic elegance with modern comforts. This picture perfect property offers a large city lot and plenty of interior space.  inside you will find a cozy living room, dining room and spacious kitchen. The owner's bedroom is located on the first floor, and four additional bedrooms and an office space upstairs. Outside offers a large front porch,  and a patio off the kitchen perfect for entertaining. Don't miss your chance to own this lovely home in a convenient location. Schedule your private showing today!
